title: Developers Looking To Build 'The Next' Disney World In CG! | Qui West | 99.1 KGGI
text:
share 
According to PinalCentral , "Mickey Mouse may have a competitor in central Arizona if a new development project under review by the city comes to fruition. 
The plans submitted to the city in January describe the project to be similar to Walt Disney World in Florida. 
“We believe we are at the same point today in Casa Grande as was Orlando 50 years ago when Walt Disney envisioned Disney World,” the plan says. 
(SOURCE: PinalCentral ) Project to be reviewed by the Casa Grande Planning and Zoning Commission on March 2nd.
